  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308980/extras/166eaf326d6c7ebb9d1a6b4438a82694.avif?t=1598381621\" width=616 height=77 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story:</h2>The unknown and magical appearance of dungeons, one day, transforms your world. Your kingdom, your home, is destroyed. The few survivors are trapped and deprived of liberty. Your bravery and adventurous spirit that characterize you will help achieve your escape, rescue prisoners and destroy the dungeons in this world full of <strong>action, magic and fantasy</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural generation:</h2>From decorations to entire layouts each dungeon you visit will be <strong>unique</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic lighting:</h2>May those pixels shine!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Artifacts:</h2>Gather artifacts from the dungeons you raid and improve throughout your adventure.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use different spells:</h2>Slay your enemies in different ways, adapt to every situation<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308980/extras/6593ee53aacc4cfac33828cf25147a52.poster.avif?t=1598381621\" width=300 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308980/extras/6593ee53aacc4cfac33828cf25147a52.webm?t=1598381621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308980/extras/6593ee53aacc4cfac33828cf25147a52.mp4?t=1598381621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308980/extras/506ee15b0af4ea8be086f99d06156a2a.poster.avif?t=1598381621\" width=300 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.s